overview: Monogram's Outlaws of Texas is surprisingly bereft of the action highlights one might expect from star Whip Wilson. This time, the Whip and his saddle pal Andy Clyde play heroes Tom and Hungry who work undercover to break up a gang of bank robbers.
tagline: GUN THUNDER ROCKS THE PANHANDLE! Fighting Marshal joins outlaw band for six-gun clean-up of killers!
title: Outlaws of Texas
